Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有星光的迷宫里挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:30.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受灵魂的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙正在呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:47.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负伤痕 知晓孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:52.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了羁绊的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除阴翳眼眸中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:04.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:14.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背负的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够称为爱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们相互支持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为风的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的Ω神话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:31.40,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.00,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位同学是天鹰座Aquila的尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们这个年龄上最优秀的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会详细教给你Palaestra的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及作为圣斗士的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是幼狮座Lionet的苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在解读你的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从星辰的运动可以知道各种各样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并能进行预测
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人从星辰中诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运也被其左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于拥有守护星座的圣斗士 更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座和幼狮座的星象不合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相性极差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈焰风暴席卷而起！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜与苍摩的友情！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座 天鹰座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢…竟然敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨托涅君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧罗巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么您会来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很不甘心失败吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能更强一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你 墨托涅君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想要力量的话 就给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是黑之沙漏·反限（Anti-limit）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会收下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸至极
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:03:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨托涅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到幼狮座和天鹰座了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我们的钩爪把他们刺穿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁闪箭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人聚集了相当多的战斗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法把那扇门击破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚固的门 大量的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是进入帕拉斯城的捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 突击了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说这是通往帕拉斯城的捷径么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要突击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也是在全力防守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面还有很长的路要走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不制定作战计划谨慎前进的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体和圣衣都会承受不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能磨磨蹭蹭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在想作战计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来增援的圣斗士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小宇宙的感觉 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刻斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴之间意见出现分歧 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在争吵着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜至极 能像我们这样友好相处就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是强大而美丽的尤弥尔姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不是为姐姐着想的温柔的弟弟 墨托涅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是三级刻斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钩爪·至高辉煌（Claw Max Brilliant）的尤弥尔和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的弟弟墨托涅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帕拉斯大人美丽的奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们攻击了自己的刻斗士同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西我们不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我和姐姐在就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座 天鹰座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要一雪前耻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要打败你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不接受教训的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来几次也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨托涅？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可不会像上次一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨托涅 那个莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要与强大而美丽的姐姐相般配的 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 墨托涅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发自内心地爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的小宇宙… 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的生命被吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走对方的时间 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是这黑色沙漏·反限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨托涅 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都更美丽 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且比任何人都更强大的尤弥尔姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最亲爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我融为一体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨…托…涅…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到姐姐的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就永远在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么人啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟把自己的姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 对不起 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我和姐姐必须要比任何人都更美丽 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我绝对不会原谅这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管付出多大的牺牲我都必须打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会理解我的吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你们的错 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有你们的话 姐姐就不用死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡扯什么 凶手不正是你自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 没用的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他已经不能正常对话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一张脸 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的武器 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一条性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐终于融合为同一具肉体了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可谓一心同体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要忘了还有我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太碍事了 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡之爪（Death Claw）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标只有你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我与姐姐爱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 墨托涅的目标是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门已经被破坏 道路打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 你们先前进 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就交给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要活下来再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座 天鹰座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧 刻斗士们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由雅典娜的圣斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我海蛇座的市大人来做你们的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞毛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能拖累大家 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去宽敞的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鹰抓小鸡已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们来做你的对手 墨托涅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮炽焰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击被抵消了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的力量就只有这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就是因为这种程度的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝我和姐姐的怒火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤弥尔姐姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们两个人的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负还没分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为我的钩爪·至高辉煌下的亡魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一个人冲过来才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你个痛快的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不痛不痒的踢法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们终归只有一个人的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:41.13,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜和苍摩、友情之炎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没事吧 尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相性极差吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往后的日子真值得期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相性好的人 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相性差的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合得来的人 合不来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候也确实让人窝火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我最喜欢的就是这各种人都存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为那些星星全都不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能够占星的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上有这么多星星 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但每一个都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炽热的星星 冰冷的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大星星 小星星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么多星星汇聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就组成了一个星座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们就受到那星光的庇佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了守护雅典娜的世界的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 在同一时代成为圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是星星的指引吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座的尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你多关照 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座的苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条腿 看起来伤得很重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连站都站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今你不过是一只折翼的鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伙伴已经废了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃那个累赘 自己去逃命如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会听你的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明杀了天鹰座一个我就会解气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又能平安跑路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真顽强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明扔下天鹰座逃走才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 你先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的刻斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来独自打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 不愧是尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是被这种家伙乱说 还会沉默的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你可别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我会是那种丢下受伤的同伴 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己跑路的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你俩感情还真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啥关系哟？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是雅典娜的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在Palaestra共同切磋技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来合力守护世界的的同伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的同伴 终归不过是路人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可无法匹敌我们的姐弟之情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要反抗吗 愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的是你啊 墨托涅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你这话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若无其事地抛弃刻斗士同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只顾自己方便 毫无同情之心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界并非只是围绕自己而转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们如果独自一人 便无法生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更无法去守护世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 才要和同伴共同生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受同伴 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信同伴 并相互帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认同这些的你 才是愚蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我才不需要什么无聊的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有姐姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着强烈的爱之羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并没有什么爱和羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了满足自己的欲望 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺去了姐姐的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不是爱和羁绊 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是任性而卑鄙的背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 给我住口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道我和姐姐的什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你们只是没有血缘关系的路人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁 最初也都只是路人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们踏过无数战场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同开拓命运至今
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是雅典娜的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在星光的指引下 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着绝不会被斩断的羁绊支撑着我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强词夺理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让你们见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的羁绊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本只有姐弟二人合力才能使用的双子狂乱钩爪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我一人也可以驾驭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天鹰座Aquila的尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便折断羽翼 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便身处狂风暴雨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起舞吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风暴啊 撕裂那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双子狂乱钩爪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由之风啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示你的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风暴龙卷风（Storm Tornado）！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种强度的风 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言 不过是微风拂面而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无力飞翔的天鹰座 又能搞出什么花样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要起飞的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座的风将幼狮座送上了高空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰迎风则愈旺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人的风 助我的火焰愈燃愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小宇宙！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮耀斑风暴轰炸（Lionet Flare Storm Bomber）！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量提升后的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被区区青铜击败…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不在我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙太狂妄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才迫不得已…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她很愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情何以堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这般努力甚至搭上了姐姐的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却遭到反击而败北
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 实乃悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨托涅君 好可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是好可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一场表演好像快开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次能观赏到什么样的演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼哼 让人好生期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.80,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼座 门卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 你这身圣衣不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光的 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很漂亮哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮得想要破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然仅凭一击 就毁掉了白银圣衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 要破坏什么样的圣衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其疾如风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要对阵的家伙和以往遇到的不可同日而语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不着刻衣出现在我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他动作如蝶一般飞舞 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击如蜜蜂刺蜇同样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的圣衣瞬间遭到破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣破坏者！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编外刻斗士来袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗
